WEBVTT

00:00:07.368 --> 00:00:08.135
[<i>Uragiri no Yuyake</i>

00:00:08.135 --> 00:00:09.704
by Theater Brook]

00:00:09.704 --> 00:00:12.706
&gt;&gt; ♪ [singing in Japanese] ♪

00:00:12.706 --> 00:00:20.746
♪ ♪

00:01:14.594 --> 00:01:16.429
&gt;&gt; THAT WAS, LIKE, A CONVENIENCE

00:01:16.429 --> 00:01:17.230
STORE TRASH CAN.

00:01:17.230 --> 00:01:18.564
&gt;&gt; WHATEVER YOU DO, STAY AWAY

00:01:18.564 --> 00:01:20.199
FROM SHIZUO HEIWAJIMA.

00:01:20.199 --> 00:01:21.367
&gt;&gt; YOU KNOW, THE PROBLEM WITH

00:01:21.367 --> 00:01:22.901
YOU, SHIZU-CHAN, IS THAT YOU

00:01:22.901 --> 00:01:24.369
CAN’T BE SWAYED BY REASON,

00:01:24.369 --> 00:01:25.370
AND THAT’S BAD.

00:01:25.370 --> 00:01:26.738
&gt;&gt; DIDN’T I TELL YOU NEVER TO

00:01:26.738 --> 00:01:28.940
SET FOOT IN IKEBUKURO AGAIN?

00:01:28.940 --> 00:01:30.408
&gt;&gt; SHIZUO!

00:01:30.408 --> 00:01:32.476
FIGHTING ALWAYS BAD!

00:01:32.476 --> 00:01:33.577
&gt;&gt; SHUT UP!

00:01:33.577 --> 00:01:34.578
&gt;&gt; WHAT?

00:01:34.578 --> 00:01:35.612
THE TOUGHEST GUY IN IKEBUKURO?

00:01:35.612 --> 00:01:36.880
&gt;&gt; OH, NO, IT’S GOTTA BE THAT

00:01:36.880 --> 00:01:37.881
OTHER CAT--

00:01:37.881 --> 00:01:39.816
&gt;&gt; all: SHIZUO HEIWAJIMA!

00:01:39.816 --> 00:01:42.819
&gt;&gt; ♪ [singing in Japanese] ♪

00:01:42.819 --> 00:01:50.860
♪ ♪

00:02:06.674 --> 00:02:07.908
&gt;&gt; THEY JUST LIKE FIRED ME FOR

00:02:07.908 --> 00:02:08.775
NOTHING.

00:02:08.775 --> 00:02:09.942
AND THEY KICKED ME OUT OF MY

00:02:09.942 --> 00:02:11.544
COMPANY HOUSING TOO.

00:02:11.544 --> 00:02:12.879
NOT TO MENTION NO SEVERANCE

00:02:12.879 --> 00:02:13.546
PAY.

00:02:13.546 --> 00:02:14.580
NOW I’VE GOT NO MONEY, NO FOOD,

00:02:14.580 --> 00:02:15.481
NO NOTHING.

00:02:15.481 --> 00:02:16.615
AND YOU THINK THE GOVERNMENT’S

00:02:16.615 --> 00:02:17.549
GONNA HELP A GUY LIKE ME OUT?

00:02:17.549 --> 00:02:18.550
I DON’T THINK SO.

00:02:18.550 --> 00:02:19.618
IT’S THE GOVERNMENT’S FAULT...

00:02:19.618 --> 00:02:20.218
&gt;&gt; SHUT UP.

00:02:20.218 --> 00:02:20.952
&gt;&gt; THAT I’M IN THIS SPOT TO

00:02:20.952 --> 00:02:21.553
BEGIN WITH.

00:02:21.553 --> 00:02:22.621
&gt;&gt; SO YOU BORROWED MONEY TO BANG

00:02:22.621 --> 00:02:23.922
SOME BATHHOUSE CHICK?

00:02:23.922 --> 00:02:24.689
&gt;&gt; IT’S LOVE.

00:02:24.689 --> 00:02:26.991
SHE’S NOT JUST SOME CHICK.

00:02:26.991 --> 00:02:29.326
MINT AND I HAVE TRUE LOVE.

00:02:29.326 --> 00:02:29.794
&gt;&gt; HUH?

00:02:29.794 --> 00:02:30.728
&gt;&gt; YOU’RE BUGGIN’.

00:02:30.728 --> 00:02:32.229
&gt;&gt; I DON’T HAVE HER NUMBER.

00:02:32.229 --> 00:02:34.464
AND I CAN ONLY SEE HER AT WORK.

00:02:34.464 --> 00:02:35.299
BUT I MEAN IT.

00:02:35.299 --> 00:02:38.635
WHAT WE HAVE IS REAL.

00:02:38.635 --> 00:02:41.237
&gt;&gt; YOU PISS ME OFF!

00:02:41.237 --> 00:02:42.505
THE ONLY TIME THIS GIRL WILL

00:02:42.505 --> 00:02:43.739
SEE YOU IS AT THE BATHHOUSE?

00:02:43.739 --> 00:02:44.740
AND SHE HASN’T EVEN GIVEN YOU

00:02:44.740 --> 00:02:45.508
HER PHONE NUMBER?

00:02:45.508 --> 00:02:46.709
&gt;&gt; [whimpering]

00:02:46.709 --> 00:02:47.810
&gt;&gt; LET ME SAY THIS UP FRONT.

00:02:47.810 --> 00:02:50.012
YOU’RE TELLING ME...

00:02:50.012 --> 00:02:51.246
YOU REALLY THINK...

00:02:51.246 --> 00:02:53.381
&gt;&gt; OH, BOY.

00:02:53.381 --> 00:02:54.015
&gt;&gt; THAT’S "TRUE LOVE?"

00:02:54.015 --> 00:02:57.651
&gt;&gt; AH!

00:02:57.651 --> 00:03:00.387
&gt;&gt; I REALLY HATE VIOLENCE.

00:03:03.724 --> 00:03:04.991
&gt;&gt; HAVE YOU HEARD?

00:03:04.991 --> 00:03:06.759
THAT SHIZUO GUY HAS BEEN ON A

00:03:06.759 --> 00:03:08.294
RAMPAGE LATELY.

00:03:08.294 --> 00:03:09.529
SOMETHING’S GOT HIM SUPER PISSED

00:03:09.529 --> 00:03:10.696
OFF.

00:03:10.696 --> 00:03:11.764
&gt;&gt; WHAT?

00:03:11.764 --> 00:03:12.898
&gt;&gt; YOU MEAN THAT GUY WHO DRESSES

00:03:12.898 --> 00:03:14.633
LIKE A BARTENDER.

00:03:14.633 --> 00:03:15.834
SHIZUO HEIWAJIMA?

00:03:15.834 --> 00:03:16.701
&gt;&gt; YEAH.

00:03:16.701 --> 00:03:17.736
&gt;&gt; HE’S ALWAYS BEEN PRETTY

00:03:17.736 --> 00:03:18.603
SCARY.

00:03:18.603 --> 00:03:19.838
BUT LATELY, HE’S GOTTEN MUCH

00:03:19.838 --> 00:03:21.606
WORSE.

00:03:21.606 --> 00:03:22.907
THEY SAY IKEBUKURO IS A TOTAL

00:03:22.907 --> 00:03:24.708
WAR ZONE RIGHT NOW.

00:03:24.708 --> 00:03:27.378
&gt;&gt; YOU KNOW, I SAW HIM ONCE.

00:03:27.378 --> 00:03:29.012
HE IS KIND OF SCARY.

00:03:29.012 --> 00:03:31.781
HE COULD DO SOME SERIOUS DAMAGE.

00:03:31.781 --> 00:03:33.016
&gt;&gt; I DON’T KNOW.

00:03:33.016 --> 00:03:34.551
WE SHOULDN’T GO ASSUMING THINGS

00:03:34.551 --> 00:03:36.619
WE HAVEN’T SEEN FOR OURSELVES.

00:03:36.619 --> 00:03:37.854
&gt;&gt; WHY ARE YOU STICKING UP FOR

00:03:37.854 --> 00:03:38.620
HIM, SETTON?

00:03:38.620 --> 00:03:39.822
DO YOU KNOW HIM?

00:03:39.822 --> 00:03:41.290
&gt;&gt; OR MAYBE YOU’RE IN WITH THE

00:03:41.290 --> 00:03:41.790
YAKUZA?

00:03:41.790 --> 00:03:43.459
OH, YOU’RE SCARY!

00:03:43.459 --> 00:03:44.693
SAVE ME!

00:03:44.693 --> 00:03:47.662
&gt;&gt; THAT’S NOT IT.

00:03:47.662 --> 00:03:49.064
&gt;&gt; COME ON, MAN, CHILL OUT.

00:03:49.064 --> 00:03:50.565
WE CAN’T COLLECT ANYTHING IF YOU

00:03:50.565 --> 00:03:51.666
KEEP SMASHING PEOPLE INTO THE

00:03:51.666 --> 00:03:53.801
WALLS ALL THE TIME.

00:03:53.801 --> 00:03:54.869
&gt;&gt; SORRY.

00:03:54.869 --> 00:03:57.904
SMELLS LIKE SHIT.

00:03:57.904 --> 00:04:01.040
[loud explosion]

00:04:01.040 --> 00:04:03.009
&gt;&gt; [sighs]

00:04:03.009 --> 00:04:04.443
&gt;&gt; THEY SAID HE HASN’T BEEN HOME

00:04:04.443 --> 00:04:06.712
FOR TWO OR THREE DAYS.

00:04:06.712 --> 00:04:07.546
BEEN HEARING A LOT OF THAT

00:04:07.546 --> 00:04:08.581
LATELY.

00:04:08.581 --> 00:04:09.448
IT’S GOTTA BE THE HUMAN

00:04:09.448 --> 00:04:12.450
TRAFFICKERS.

00:04:12.450 --> 00:04:14.619
&gt;&gt; SMELLS LIKE SHIT.

00:04:19.090 --> 00:04:21.758
&gt;&gt; WHOA, THAT GUY’S REALLY HURT.

00:04:21.758 --> 00:04:23.794
THEY SAID IT WAS THE SLASHER.

00:04:23.794 --> 00:04:24.695
&gt;&gt; JUST NOW?

00:04:24.695 --> 00:04:25.862
&gt;&gt; YEAH, I SAW IT.

00:04:25.862 --> 00:04:28.364
IT RAN THAT WAY.

00:04:28.364 --> 00:04:29.732
&gt;&gt; [sighs]

00:04:29.732 --> 00:04:31.034
’BUKURO IS JUST GETTING CRAZIER

00:04:31.034 --> 00:04:32.902
BY THE DAY.

00:04:32.902 --> 00:04:35.771
&gt;&gt; [gasps]

00:04:37.072 --> 00:04:39.808
&gt;&gt; MORE SHIT.

00:04:43.778 --> 00:04:45.079
THIS WHOLE FREAKIN’ TOWN SMELLS

00:04:45.079 --> 00:04:46.948
LIKE SHIT.

00:04:46.948 --> 00:04:48.649
WHATEVER IT IS, IT PISSES ME

00:04:48.649 --> 00:04:49.950
OFF.

00:04:49.950 --> 00:04:50.818
&gt;&gt; WELL, NOW,

00:04:50.818 --> 00:04:52.753
IT’S SHIZUO AND MR. TOM.

00:04:52.753 --> 00:04:56.789
&gt;&gt; HEY, SIMON.

00:04:56.789 --> 00:04:58.358
&gt;&gt; SHIZUO?

00:04:58.358 --> 00:04:59.792
&gt;&gt; SORRY, HE’S BEEN KIND OF

00:04:59.792 --> 00:05:01.594
CRANKY LATELY.

00:05:01.594 --> 00:05:02.762
&gt;&gt; SHIZUO, I THINK LIKE HE IN

00:05:02.762 --> 00:05:04.630
PUBERTY?

00:05:04.630 --> 00:05:05.964
&gt;&gt; KIND OF.

00:05:05.964 --> 00:05:09.100
MORE LIKE A REBEL, I GUESS.

00:05:09.100 --> 00:05:12.137
&gt;&gt; LIKE REBEL?

00:05:12.137 --> 00:05:13.571
&gt;&gt; HEY.

00:05:13.571 --> 00:05:17.642
LONG TIME, NO SEE.

00:05:17.642 --> 00:05:20.744
HMM.

00:05:28.852 --> 00:05:30.086
&gt;&gt; SO LOOKS LIKE HE’S GONNA

00:05:30.086 --> 00:05:32.020
BE STARRING IN ANOTHER MOVIE.

00:05:32.020 --> 00:05:33.522
YUHEI HANEJIMA SURE IS POPULAR

00:05:33.522 --> 00:05:35.490
RIGHT NOW.

00:05:35.490 --> 00:05:38.793
I MEAN, KASUKA HEIWAJIMA.

00:05:39.894 --> 00:05:41.396
BEING HIS OLDER BROTHER MUST

00:05:41.396 --> 00:05:43.898
MAKE YOU PRETTY PROUD, SHIZUO

00:05:43.898 --> 00:05:46.967
HEIWAJIMA.

00:05:46.967 --> 00:05:49.836
SORRY, I’M SHUJI NIEKAWA.

00:05:49.836 --> 00:05:52.638
HERE’S MY CARD.

00:05:52.638 --> 00:05:53.739
HIS GOOD LOOKS DEFINITELY DON’T

00:05:53.739 --> 00:05:54.740
HURT HIM.

00:05:54.740 --> 00:05:55.975
BUT HE ALSO HAPPENS TO BE A

00:05:55.975 --> 00:05:57.910
PRETTY GOOD ACTOR.

00:05:57.910 --> 00:05:59.679
WHAT WAS IT?

00:05:59.679 --> 00:06:00.913
THE NAME OF THE FIRST BIG MOVIE

00:06:00.913 --> 00:06:02.047
HE DID?

00:06:02.047 --> 00:06:03.682
OH, YEAH.

00:06:03.682 --> 00:06:04.649
THAT’S RIGHT.

00:06:04.649 --> 00:06:06.150
IT WAS <i>VAMPIRE NINJA CARMILLA</i>

00:06:06.150 --> 00:06:07.752
<i>SAIZOU.</i>

00:06:07.752 --> 00:06:10.955
[dramatic music]

00:06:10.955 --> 00:06:14.458
♪ ♪

00:06:14.458 --> 00:06:16.627
[explosion]

00:06:19.896 --> 00:06:21.864
&gt;&gt; I KNEW RIGHT AWAY THAT KID

00:06:21.864 --> 00:06:23.666
WAS GOING TO BE BIG.

00:06:23.666 --> 00:06:24.767
AND FROM EVERYTHING I’VE READ,

00:06:24.767 --> 00:06:26.002
HE EVEN DID HIS OWN STUNTS IN

00:06:26.002 --> 00:06:27.803
THAT MOVIE.

00:06:27.803 --> 00:06:28.804
THERE ARE SOME PEOPLE OUT THERE

00:06:28.804 --> 00:06:30.906
WHO SAY YOU TAUGHT HIM THAT.

00:06:30.906 --> 00:06:32.140
IF YOU EVER WANT TO TALK A

00:06:32.140 --> 00:06:34.175
LITTLE BIT ABOUT IT, I’D LOVE TO

00:06:34.175 --> 00:06:35.210
HEAR IT.

00:06:35.210 --> 00:06:38.946
[cigarette cracking]

00:06:38.946 --> 00:06:40.014
&gt;&gt; AH, DAMN!

00:06:40.014 --> 00:06:44.451
&gt;&gt; [angry yell]

00:06:44.451 --> 00:06:47.987
[loud thud]

00:06:47.987 --> 00:06:51.557
&gt;&gt; [heavy breathing]

00:06:51.557 --> 00:06:53.492
&gt;&gt; EARLIER, WHEN I SAID THAT

00:06:53.492 --> 00:06:56.862
I HATE VIOLENCE, I MEANT THAT.

00:06:56.862 --> 00:06:58.130
TRUTH IS, I HAVEN’T ALWAYS BEEN

00:06:58.130 --> 00:07:00.165
THIS WAY.

00:07:00.165 --> 00:07:03.901
[spoon snapping]

00:07:03.901 --> 00:07:04.936
THE FIRST TIME I GOT IN A

00:07:04.936 --> 00:07:06.237
FIGHT WAS WITH MY LITTLE

00:07:06.237 --> 00:07:07.639
BROTHER, KASUKA.

00:07:07.639 --> 00:07:08.105
[struggling]

00:07:08.105 --> 00:07:09.974
IT WAS OVER SOMETHING STUPID.

00:07:09.974 --> 00:07:11.208
BUT I SNAPPED AND TRIED TO HURL

00:07:11.208 --> 00:07:12.909
A REFRIGERATOR AT HIM.

00:07:12.909 --> 00:07:17.047
[cracking]

00:07:17.047 --> 00:07:19.149
&gt;&gt; [swallowing]

00:07:19.149 --> 00:07:20.049
[sighs]

00:07:26.521 --> 00:07:28.723
&gt;&gt; THE REFRIGERATOR IDEA WASN’T

00:07:28.723 --> 00:07:30.592
A CONSCIOUS ONE.

00:07:30.592 --> 00:07:32.260
MY BODY JUST SORT OF WENT INTO

00:07:32.260 --> 00:07:34.195
AUTO-PILOT.

00:07:34.195 --> 00:07:35.263
AFTER THAT...

00:07:35.263 --> 00:07:37.765
&gt;&gt; [singing] SHIZUO’S A LAME-O!

00:07:37.765 --> 00:07:38.699
LAME-O!

00:07:38.699 --> 00:07:41.268
STUPID, STUPID LAME-O!

00:07:41.268 --> 00:07:42.635
[pencil snapping]

00:07:42.635 --> 00:07:44.804
&gt;&gt; [laughter]

00:07:44.804 --> 00:07:46.873
&gt;&gt; I COULDN’T HELP MYSELF.

00:07:46.873 --> 00:07:48.708
WHEN I GOT MAD, MY BODY JUST

00:07:48.708 --> 00:07:49.709
STARTED TO MOVE ON ITS OWN.

00:07:49.709 --> 00:07:50.209
&gt;&gt; AHH!

00:07:50.209 --> 00:07:54.580
[crash]

00:07:57.883 --> 00:07:59.117
&gt;&gt; [laughs]

00:07:59.117 --> 00:08:01.552
&gt;&gt; AND EACH TIME IT HAPPENED...

00:08:14.263 --> 00:08:15.899
&gt;&gt; HUMANS CAN GET EXTRA STRONG

00:08:15.899 --> 00:08:16.632
IN A CRISIS.

00:08:16.632 --> 00:08:17.700
BUT I THINK YOU’RE DIFFERENT.

00:08:17.700 --> 00:08:18.834
I THINK YOU CAN ALWAYS GET

00:08:18.834 --> 00:08:19.802
THERE.

00:08:19.802 --> 00:08:20.869
A NORMAL PERSON’S BRAIN LIMITS

00:08:20.869 --> 00:08:21.870
THEIR STRENGTH.

00:08:21.870 --> 00:08:23.806
BECAUSE IF YOU DIDN’T HOLD BACK,

00:08:23.806 --> 00:08:24.907
YOU’D DESTROY YOUR MUSCLES AND

00:08:24.907 --> 00:08:26.541
BONES.

00:08:26.541 --> 00:08:27.909
BUT YOUR BRAIN BEHAVES

00:08:27.909 --> 00:08:28.576
DIFFERENTLY.

00:08:28.576 --> 00:08:29.977
IT LETS YOUR BODY GO WILD.

00:08:29.977 --> 00:08:31.012
IT’S A MYSTERIOUS WONDER LIKE NO

00:08:31.012 --> 00:08:31.879
OTHER.

00:08:31.879 --> 00:08:32.746
YOU’RE LIKE SOME KIND OF

00:08:32.746 --> 00:08:34.048
SCIENTIFIC DISCOVERY.

00:08:34.048 --> 00:08:35.316
YOU KNOW WHAT?

00:08:35.316 --> 00:08:36.217
IF YOU WERE TO LET ME TRY AND

00:08:36.217 --> 00:08:36.783
DISSECT--

00:08:36.783 --> 00:08:37.851
HUH?

00:08:37.851 --> 00:08:39.986
[groaning]

00:08:39.986 --> 00:08:41.087
THAT HURTS.

00:08:41.087 --> 00:08:42.688
SHIZUO, THAT HURTS.

00:08:42.688 --> 00:08:44.690
&gt;&gt; I DON’T KNOW HOW IT WORKS.

00:08:44.690 --> 00:08:45.925
I JUST KNOW I CAN’T CONTROL MY

00:08:45.925 --> 00:08:46.926
ANGER.

00:08:46.926 --> 00:08:48.160
AND WHEN I DO GET ANGRY, I

00:08:48.160 --> 00:08:49.761
DESTROY EVERYTHING, INCLUDING MY

00:08:49.761 --> 00:08:51.963
OWN BODY.

00:08:51.963 --> 00:08:53.965
THAT’S ALL I’VE LEARNED.

00:08:53.965 --> 00:08:57.201
&gt;&gt; [pained screams]

00:08:57.201 --> 00:08:58.669
&gt;&gt; SO SINCE THEN...

00:08:58.669 --> 00:08:59.937
[explosion]

00:08:59.937 --> 00:09:02.305
I’VE STOPPED HOLDING BACK.

00:09:02.305 --> 00:09:03.741
IF I COULDN’T DO IT ANYWAY, WHY

00:09:03.741 --> 00:09:05.242
BOTHER TRYING.

00:09:05.242 --> 00:09:06.043
BROKEN BONES?

00:09:06.043 --> 00:09:07.177
HA!

00:09:07.177 --> 00:09:08.611
WHO GIVES A DAMN?

00:09:08.611 --> 00:09:10.580
[explosion]

00:09:10.580 --> 00:09:11.848
I’VE WRECKED MY BODY A THOUSAND

00:09:11.848 --> 00:09:13.149
TIMES NOW.

00:09:13.149 --> 00:09:14.616
AND EACH TIME I COME BACK

00:09:14.616 --> 00:09:16.085
STRONGER.

00:09:16.085 --> 00:09:17.219
SHINRA ONCE SAID...

00:09:17.219 --> 00:09:18.687
YOU KNOW WHAT, SCREW WHAT HE

00:09:18.687 --> 00:09:19.320
SAID.

00:09:19.320 --> 00:09:21.990
I COME BACK TOUGHER EVERY TIME.

00:09:21.990 --> 00:09:23.992
[chiming]

00:09:23.992 --> 00:09:26.261
BUT STILL...

00:09:26.261 --> 00:09:28.963
&gt;&gt; HEY...

00:09:28.963 --> 00:09:29.930
YOU SEEM TO GET HURT AN AWFUL

00:09:29.930 --> 00:09:30.798
LOT.

00:09:30.798 --> 00:09:33.300
ARE YOU OKAY?

00:09:33.300 --> 00:09:35.269
STAY RIGHT THERE.

00:09:37.737 --> 00:09:39.605
HERE YOU GO.

00:09:39.605 --> 00:09:40.839
YOU NEED TO DRINK SOME MILK AND

00:09:40.839 --> 00:09:41.907
STRENGTHEN THOSE BONES.

00:09:41.907 --> 00:09:44.176
SAME FOR YOU.

00:09:44.176 --> 00:09:47.880
&gt;&gt; THANK YOU.

00:09:47.880 --> 00:09:50.182
&gt;&gt; [laughs]

00:09:50.182 --> 00:09:52.617
[sentimental music]

00:09:52.617 --> 00:09:59.923
♪ ♪

00:10:04.928 --> 00:10:07.297
&gt;&gt; [sighs, chuckles]

00:10:07.297 --> 00:10:09.932
&gt;&gt; [murmurs]

00:10:09.932 --> 00:10:12.935
[chiming]

00:10:12.935 --> 00:10:17.005
[train lightly rumbling]

00:10:22.143 --> 00:10:27.080
[chiming]

00:10:27.080 --> 00:10:29.850
&gt;&gt; [groans]

00:10:29.850 --> 00:10:32.952
[bells ringing]

00:10:32.952 --> 00:10:34.854
[snaps]

00:10:40.659 --> 00:10:46.697
[heavy breathing]

00:10:50.000 --> 00:10:51.869
&gt;&gt; I HAD SCREWED UP.

00:10:51.869 --> 00:10:53.704
I DIDN’T MEAN TO.

00:10:53.704 --> 00:10:54.238
BUT THEN I NEVER DO.

00:10:54.238 --> 00:10:55.172
&gt;&gt; GOOD MORNING!

00:10:55.172 --> 00:10:58.174
[sentimental music]

00:10:58.174 --> 00:11:02.245
♪ ♪

00:11:02.245 --> 00:11:05.014
&gt;&gt; WHY DID THIS HAPPEN?

00:11:05.014 --> 00:11:07.450
MY FAMILY WAS BASICALLY NORMAL.

00:11:07.450 --> 00:11:08.417
IT’S NOT LIKE I HAD SOME BIG

00:11:08.417 --> 00:11:10.953
TRAUMA IN MY LIFE.

00:11:10.953 --> 00:11:12.020
AND YET...

00:11:12.020 --> 00:11:15.022
&gt;&gt; KASUKA.

00:11:15.022 --> 00:11:18.159
&gt;&gt; YEAH.

00:11:18.159 --> 00:11:19.460
&gt;&gt; DON’T YOU...EVER GET SCARED

00:11:19.460 --> 00:11:23.397
OF ME?

00:11:23.397 --> 00:11:25.932
&gt;&gt; NOT REALLY.

00:11:29.002 --> 00:11:31.204
[distant horns honk]

00:11:31.204 --> 00:11:32.237
&gt;&gt; HMM.

00:11:38.043 --> 00:11:39.311
&gt;&gt; IT WASN’T UNTIL I ENTERED

00:11:39.311 --> 00:11:40.712
RAIRA THAT IT HIT ME.

00:11:40.712 --> 00:11:42.981
&gt;&gt; GRAND OPENING DISCOUNT SALE.

00:11:42.981 --> 00:11:44.348
THE SHOP IS FRESH.

00:11:44.348 --> 00:11:45.216
THE FISH ARE FRESH.

00:11:45.216 --> 00:11:46.217
&gt;&gt; HEY, WE’RE GOING TO THE SAME

00:11:46.217 --> 00:11:47.118
SCHOOL AGAIN.

00:11:47.118 --> 00:11:48.286
KIND OF FEELS LIKE FATE, DOESN’T

00:11:48.286 --> 00:11:49.453
IT?

00:11:49.453 --> 00:11:50.988
&gt;&gt; SHUT YOUR HOLE.

00:11:50.988 --> 00:11:51.889
&gt;&gt; HEY...

00:11:51.889 --> 00:11:53.123
HOW’S YOUR BODY HOLDING UP?

00:11:53.123 --> 00:11:53.991
I KNOW!

00:11:53.991 --> 00:11:55.025
YOU COULD LET ME GIVE YOU AN

00:11:55.025 --> 00:11:57.026
EXAM.

00:11:57.026 --> 00:11:59.095
SO NO?

00:11:59.095 --> 00:11:59.962
OKAY, THEN.

00:11:59.962 --> 00:12:02.298
HOW ABOUT A BLOOD SAMPLE?

00:12:02.298 --> 00:12:05.267
&gt;&gt; CELTY!

00:12:05.267 --> 00:12:07.435
WHAT HAPPENED YESTERDAY?

00:12:07.435 --> 00:12:08.904
WHEN YOU DIDN’T COME HOME, I WAS

00:12:08.904 --> 00:12:10.071
WORRIED.

00:12:10.071 --> 00:12:11.139
WERE YOU TRYING TO TRACK DOWN

00:12:11.139 --> 00:12:13.874
YOUR HEAD AGAIN?

00:12:13.874 --> 00:12:14.375
YEAH, RIGHT!

00:12:14.375 --> 00:12:15.776
I BET YOU MET A GUY, AND YOU

00:12:15.776 --> 00:12:17.211
WERE OUT--

00:12:17.211 --> 00:12:20.347
[groaning] OH, CELTY...

00:12:20.347 --> 00:12:22.916
WOULD YOU STOP PUNCHING ME?

00:12:22.916 --> 00:12:24.518
OKAY, OKAY, CELTY.

00:12:24.518 --> 00:12:25.318
I’LL INTRODUCE YOU--

00:12:25.318 --> 00:12:27.987
&gt;&gt; IT WAS THE ODDEST FEELING.

00:12:27.987 --> 00:12:29.055
I DON’T EVEN KNOW HOW TO

00:12:29.055 --> 00:12:30.456
DESCRIBE IT.

00:12:30.456 --> 00:12:32.525
IT JUST CAME OUT OF NOWHERE.

00:12:32.525 --> 00:12:35.961
&gt;&gt; SOMEDAY I’M GOING TO MARRY--

00:12:35.961 --> 00:12:36.894
&gt;&gt; I’D SUDDENLY REMEMBERED

00:12:36.894 --> 00:12:39.230
SOMETHING BAD.

00:12:39.230 --> 00:12:40.765
THAT’S RIGHT.

00:12:40.765 --> 00:12:42.099
OF COURSE...

00:12:42.099 --> 00:12:43.067
IT WAS EXACTLY WHEN THAT

00:12:43.067 --> 00:12:44.201
BLOOD-SUCKING LITTLE FLEA SHOWED

00:12:44.201 --> 00:12:46.403
UP.

00:12:49.405 --> 00:12:51.241
THAT’S HIM...

00:12:51.241 --> 00:12:53.376
IZAYA ORIHARA.

00:12:53.376 --> 00:12:54.544
&gt;&gt; HUH!

00:12:54.544 --> 00:12:55.445
[maniacal laughter]

00:12:59.181 --> 00:13:03.185
[explosion]

00:13:03.185 --> 00:13:05.520
[sighs]

00:13:05.520 --> 00:13:09.357
[explosion]

00:13:09.357 --> 00:13:12.526
[heavy breathing]

00:13:12.526 --> 00:13:14.862
[clapping]

00:13:14.862 --> 00:13:15.929
&gt;&gt; AND THERE HE WAS.

00:13:15.929 --> 00:13:17.297
&gt;&gt; MEET IZAYA ORIHARA FROM OUR

00:13:17.297 --> 00:13:18.798
JUNIOR HIGH.

00:13:18.798 --> 00:13:20.167
&gt;&gt; FROM THE SECOND I SAW HIM,

00:13:20.167 --> 00:13:21.334
I HATED HIM.

00:13:21.334 --> 00:13:22.334
&gt;&gt; TO BE HONEST, HE’S NOT REALLY

00:13:22.334 --> 00:13:23.369
GOOD AT ALL.

00:13:23.369 --> 00:13:25.004
&gt;&gt; THAT ISN’T NICE, SHINRA.

00:13:25.004 --> 00:13:26.205
&gt;&gt; NO, NO.

00:13:26.205 --> 00:13:28.006
I MEANT THAT IN A GOOD WAY.

00:13:28.006 --> 00:13:29.541
&gt;&gt; YOU PISS ME OFF!

00:13:29.541 --> 00:13:30.208
&gt;&gt; NO--

00:13:30.208 --> 00:13:34.845
&gt;&gt; OH, YEAH?

00:13:34.845 --> 00:13:35.913
TOO BAD.

00:13:35.913 --> 00:13:37.147
I WAS THINKING YOU AND I COULD

00:13:37.147 --> 00:13:39.283
HAVE SOME REAL FUN TOGETHER.

00:13:39.283 --> 00:13:40.450
&gt;&gt; SHUT UP!

00:13:40.450 --> 00:13:41.886
&gt;&gt; NOW, WHY YOU GOTTA BE LIKE

00:13:41.886 --> 00:13:43.987
THAT, SHIZUO?

00:13:43.987 --> 00:13:47.090
&gt;&gt; [growling]

00:13:54.997 --> 00:13:56.331
&gt;&gt; SEE?

00:13:56.331 --> 00:14:00.402
ISN’T THIS A BLAST?

00:14:00.402 --> 00:14:01.336
&gt;&gt; HMM.

00:14:01.336 --> 00:14:02.904
&gt;&gt; AND THAT WAS IT.

00:14:02.904 --> 00:14:03.938
WE’VE BEEN TRYING TO KILL EACH

00:14:03.938 --> 00:14:05.072
OTHER FROM THE VERY FIRST DAY

00:14:05.072 --> 00:14:06.207
WE MET.

00:14:06.207 --> 00:14:07.975
THERE’S NO GOOD REASON.

00:14:07.975 --> 00:14:10.411
I JUST DON’T LIKE HIM, BUT...

00:14:10.411 --> 00:14:12.979
[tires screeching, crash]

00:14:15.949 --> 00:14:17.917
&gt;&gt; ARE YOU OKAY?

00:14:17.917 --> 00:14:18.518
&gt;&gt; IT’S ALL RIGHT.

00:14:18.518 --> 00:14:19.552
DON’T WORRY.

00:14:19.552 --> 00:14:21.053
HE’S QUITE VIRILE.

00:14:21.053 --> 00:14:22.922
&gt;&gt; UH, ARE YOU SURE WE SHOULDN’T

00:14:22.922 --> 00:14:24.123
TAKE HIM TO THE HOSPITAL?

00:14:24.123 --> 00:14:26.058
&gt;&gt; NO, NO, HE’LL BE FINE.

00:14:26.058 --> 00:14:26.958
THAT’LL BE ALL.

00:14:26.958 --> 00:14:28.860
&gt;&gt; [groans]

00:14:28.860 --> 00:14:31.262
YEAH...

00:14:31.262 --> 00:14:33.998
I SCREWED UP.

00:14:36.567 --> 00:14:38.468
[crash]

00:14:38.468 --> 00:14:41.304
&gt;&gt; [panting]

00:14:41.304 --> 00:14:43.106
&gt;&gt; OH, WHAT A COINCIDENCE.

00:14:43.106 --> 00:14:44.941
IZAYA’S HERE AS WELL.

00:14:44.941 --> 00:14:46.142
&gt;&gt; INTERESTING.

00:14:46.142 --> 00:14:48.010
HOW ARE YOU STILL STANDING?

00:14:48.010 --> 00:14:48.911
&gt;&gt; [groans]

00:14:48.911 --> 00:14:49.979
YOU’RE DEAD. YOU’RE DEAD.

00:14:49.979 --> 00:14:51.280
THAT STARTED A WHOLE CHAIN OF

00:14:51.280 --> 00:14:52.314
EVENTS.

00:14:52.314 --> 00:14:55.550
YOU ARE SO FREAKIN’ DEAD!

00:14:55.550 --> 00:14:56.251
AH!

00:14:56.251 --> 00:14:57.986
WORD GOT OUT.

00:14:57.986 --> 00:14:59.254
AND SOON EVERY GANG OF REJECTS

00:14:59.254 --> 00:15:01.422
IN THE CITY TRIED TO JUMP ME.

00:15:01.422 --> 00:15:03.057
I HADN’T DONE ANYTHING.

00:15:03.057 --> 00:15:04.024
ALL I WAS TRYING TO DO WAS LIVE

00:15:04.024 --> 00:15:07.494
A NICE, PEACEFUL LIFE.

00:15:07.494 --> 00:15:09.629
DAMN IT, DAMN IT, DAMN IT...

00:15:09.629 --> 00:15:11.998
I’M SO PISSED OFF.

00:15:11.998 --> 00:15:13.466
SHIT! SHIT!

00:15:13.466 --> 00:15:18.304
SHIT, SHIT, SHIT, SHIT, SHIT!

00:15:24.976 --> 00:15:27.111
YEAH, I KNOW.

00:15:33.984 --> 00:15:35.419
&gt;&gt; DIE!

00:15:35.419 --> 00:15:38.454
&gt;&gt; [shouting]

00:15:52.066 --> 00:15:54.268
&gt;&gt; IZAYA...

00:15:54.268 --> 00:15:55.536
HE WAS THE ONE SICCING THESE

00:15:55.536 --> 00:15:57.338
BASTARDS ON ME.

00:15:57.338 --> 00:15:58.706
WHEN I REALIZED THAT...

00:15:58.706 --> 00:16:00.608
IZAYA!

00:16:00.608 --> 00:16:03.343
[explosion]

00:16:03.343 --> 00:16:05.012
IF ONLY I COULD HAVE KILLED HIM

00:16:05.012 --> 00:16:06.179
RIGHT THEN AND THERE.

00:16:06.179 --> 00:16:09.682
DAMN IT!

00:16:09.682 --> 00:16:12.618
AFTER WE GRADUATED FROM RAIRA...

00:16:12.618 --> 00:16:15.387
&gt;&gt; SO WHAT YOU THINK?

00:16:15.387 --> 00:16:16.722
&gt;&gt; THIS IDIOT...

00:16:16.722 --> 00:16:18.089
WELL, HE’S THE SAME.

00:16:18.089 --> 00:16:19.357
BUT THAT FLEA HAS BEEN HATCHING

00:16:19.357 --> 00:16:21.226
SOMETHING WITH THE YAKUZA.

00:16:21.226 --> 00:16:22.493
BUT FOR A WHILE THERE, THINGS

00:16:22.493 --> 00:16:24.429
WERE QUIET.

00:16:24.429 --> 00:16:25.663
SO WHAT DID I DO?

00:16:25.663 --> 00:16:30.100
[growls angrily]

00:16:32.068 --> 00:16:34.538
[snarls angrily]

00:16:34.538 --> 00:16:36.472
AAH!

00:16:40.209 --> 00:16:41.710
YEAH, NONE OF THAT WORKED OUT

00:16:41.710 --> 00:16:43.612
TOO WELL.

00:16:45.613 --> 00:16:46.581
[bell ringing]

00:16:46.581 --> 00:16:49.251
&gt;&gt; COME ON IN.

00:16:52.119 --> 00:16:53.320
&gt;&gt; DID YOU SEE THAT?

00:16:53.320 --> 00:16:53.988
&gt;&gt; NO WAY!

00:16:53.988 --> 00:16:55.622
&gt;&gt; IT’S THAT ACTOR GUY.

00:16:55.622 --> 00:17:00.126
&gt;&gt; YUHEI HANEJIMA.

00:17:00.126 --> 00:17:02.062
&gt;&gt; HEY, KASUKA.

00:17:02.062 --> 00:17:04.230
WHAT BRINGS YOU HERE?

00:17:04.230 --> 00:17:07.232
HUH?

00:17:12.604 --> 00:17:14.105
A BARTENDER GETUP?

00:17:14.105 --> 00:17:15.740
&gt;&gt; YOU SHOULDN’T BE CHANGING

00:17:15.740 --> 00:17:17.408
JOBS ALL THE TIME.

00:17:17.408 --> 00:17:18.476
&gt;&gt; HUH.

00:17:18.476 --> 00:17:19.777
&gt;&gt; I BOUGHT YOU SEVERAL

00:17:19.777 --> 00:17:21.245
DIFFERENT PAIRS.

00:17:21.245 --> 00:17:22.480
THIS WAY, YOU CAN STAY HERE A

00:17:22.480 --> 00:17:25.182
WHILE.

00:17:25.182 --> 00:17:26.183
&gt;&gt; THANKS, MAN.

00:17:26.183 --> 00:17:29.052
WELL, I’LL DO MY BEST.

00:17:29.052 --> 00:17:31.388
AND SO...

00:17:31.388 --> 00:17:33.422
SON OF A...

00:17:40.095 --> 00:17:42.263
&gt;&gt; [laughs]

00:17:42.263 --> 00:17:45.100
&gt;&gt; IZAYA!

00:17:45.100 --> 00:17:49.804
THAT LITTLE MAGGOT SET ME UP.

00:17:49.804 --> 00:17:51.205
HE SLIPPED OUT OF ’BUKURO PRETTY

00:17:51.205 --> 00:17:53.040
QUICKLY.

00:17:53.040 --> 00:17:54.308
THE POLICE SOON REALIZED I WAS

00:17:54.308 --> 00:17:56.243
INNOCENT AND LET ME GO, BUT...

00:17:56.243 --> 00:17:59.045
SORRY...

00:17:59.045 --> 00:18:00.146
I DIDN’T MEAN TO BREAK MY

00:18:00.146 --> 00:18:01.647
PROMISE.

00:18:01.647 --> 00:18:03.149
&gt;&gt; HEY, SHIZUO.

00:18:03.149 --> 00:18:05.784
&gt;&gt; HMM?

00:18:08.654 --> 00:18:09.822
TOM AND I GO ALL THE WAY BACK TO

00:18:09.822 --> 00:18:11.456
JUNIOR HIGH.

00:18:11.456 --> 00:18:12.290
HE WAS STARTING A

00:18:12.290 --> 00:18:13.458
DEBT-COLLECTION AGENCY AND

00:18:13.458 --> 00:18:15.092
WANTED MY HELP.

00:18:15.092 --> 00:18:17.829
BASICALLY, I BECAME THE MUSCLE.

00:18:17.829 --> 00:18:19.596
I WASN’T INTO IT AT FIRST.

00:18:19.596 --> 00:18:21.232
THAT’S WHEN TOM SAID...

00:18:21.232 --> 00:18:22.533
&gt;&gt; LISTEN, MAN, YOU DON’T GOTTA

00:18:22.533 --> 00:18:24.467
BEAT UP ON ALL OF THEM.

00:18:24.467 --> 00:18:26.169
ONCE I SAY THE NAME

00:18:26.169 --> 00:18:28.138
SHIZUO HEIWAJIMA, MOST PEOPLE

00:18:28.138 --> 00:18:29.672
PAY UP.

00:18:29.672 --> 00:18:30.773
&gt;&gt; THAT’S WHAT HE TRIED TO TELL

00:18:30.773 --> 00:18:32.307
ME, ANYWAY.

00:18:32.307 --> 00:18:33.575
THAT WAS ALSO AROUND THE SAME

00:18:33.575 --> 00:18:35.144
TIME KASUKA STARTED GETTING

00:18:35.144 --> 00:18:36.411
BUSY.

00:18:36.411 --> 00:18:37.679
IT’S BEEN A LONG TIME SINCE

00:18:37.679 --> 00:18:40.181
I LAST SAW HIM.

00:18:40.181 --> 00:18:43.251
I WONDER IF I’VE LET HIM DOWN.

00:18:43.251 --> 00:18:44.485
&gt;&gt; WHAT’S THAT ABOUT?

00:18:44.485 --> 00:18:47.788
[crowd shouting]

00:18:47.788 --> 00:18:51.391
[cheering]

00:19:02.834 --> 00:19:07.138
&gt;&gt; HE’S SO COOL!

00:19:07.138 --> 00:19:09.740
&gt;&gt; ALL RIGHT, YUHEI!

00:19:09.740 --> 00:19:12.577
WE’RE READY!

00:19:12.577 --> 00:19:14.679
&gt;&gt; I DON’T KNOW WHY, BUT I FELT

00:19:14.679 --> 00:19:17.181
BETTER ABOUT THINGS.

00:19:17.181 --> 00:19:19.183
AND, YEAH, I’M STILL WORKING

00:19:19.183 --> 00:19:21.718
WITH TOM.

00:19:21.718 --> 00:19:23.352
&gt;&gt; REPAYMENT SCHEDULE?

00:19:23.352 --> 00:19:24.220
HUH!

00:19:24.220 --> 00:19:25.854
DUDE, WE WENT TO PUBLIC SCHOOL.

00:19:25.854 --> 00:19:27.190
I DON’T KNOW ANY OF THAT CRAP.

00:19:27.190 --> 00:19:28.524
&gt;&gt; YEAH, TOTALLY.

00:19:28.524 --> 00:19:29.625
WE’RE JUST VICTIMS OF THE

00:19:29.625 --> 00:19:31.126
SYSTEM, MAN.

00:19:31.126 --> 00:19:32.594
WE NEVER HAD A CHANCE.

00:19:32.594 --> 00:19:33.661
[laughs]

00:19:33.661 --> 00:19:34.596
&gt;&gt; ALL RIGHT, COME ON.

00:19:34.596 --> 00:19:36.298
&gt;&gt; DUDE, I TOLD YOU WE DON’T GOT

00:19:36.298 --> 00:19:37.265
IT.

00:19:37.265 --> 00:19:38.533
NOW, GET LOST, OLD MAN.

00:19:38.533 --> 00:19:39.701
&gt;&gt; SORRY, BUT THIS IS WHAT I DO

00:19:39.701 --> 00:19:40.735
FOR A LIVING.

00:19:40.735 --> 00:19:42.203
&gt;&gt; HEY, DUDE, WHAT’S THAT LOOK

00:19:42.203 --> 00:19:43.470
FOR?

00:19:43.470 --> 00:19:44.338
&gt;&gt; YO, KID...

00:19:44.338 --> 00:19:45.272
&gt;&gt; WHAT’S WITH THAT LAME-ASS

00:19:45.272 --> 00:19:46.139
GETUP?

00:19:46.139 --> 00:19:47.173
&gt;&gt; YEAH, YOU LOOK LIKE A

00:19:47.173 --> 00:19:48.574
FREAKIN’ BUTLER.

00:19:48.574 --> 00:19:49.409
&gt;&gt; WHAT ARE YOU THINKING?

00:19:49.409 --> 00:19:50.743
&gt;&gt; SERIOUSLY?

00:19:50.743 --> 00:19:52.878
YOU DON’T KNOW WHO SHIZUO IS?

00:19:52.878 --> 00:19:53.846
&gt;&gt; NO.

00:19:53.846 --> 00:19:55.548
WHAT, IS HE FAMOUS?

00:19:55.548 --> 00:19:56.916
&gt;&gt; MR. BUTLER MAN?

00:19:56.916 --> 00:19:57.582
&gt;&gt; [spits]

00:19:57.582 --> 00:19:58.717
&gt;&gt; SCORE!

00:19:58.717 --> 00:19:59.418
[laughs]

00:19:59.418 --> 00:20:00.719
WOULD YOU KINDLY BRING ME

00:20:00.719 --> 00:20:01.486
ANOTHER DRINK, PLEASE,

00:20:01.486 --> 00:20:03.388
MR. BUTLER MAN?

00:20:03.388 --> 00:20:04.656
&gt;&gt; THEY’RE IN ’BUKURO AND THEY

00:20:04.656 --> 00:20:06.224
DON’T KNOW SHIZUO.

00:20:06.224 --> 00:20:07.258
GUESS THEY DID GO TO A PUBLIC

00:20:07.258 --> 00:20:08.626
SCHOOL.

00:20:08.626 --> 00:20:11.729
[laughter]

00:20:11.729 --> 00:20:14.898
&gt;&gt; WHAT I’M WEARING WAS A GIFT

00:20:14.898 --> 00:20:18.268
FROM MY LITTLE BROTHER.

00:20:18.268 --> 00:20:20.302
[growling angrily]

00:20:24.173 --> 00:20:26.242
BUT LIKE I SAID, I REALLY HATE

00:20:26.242 --> 00:20:28.344
VIOLENCE.

00:20:28.344 --> 00:20:30.245
I JUST WANT TO GET STRONGER...

00:20:30.245 --> 00:20:32.313
STRONG ENOUGH SO THAT SOMEDAY,

00:20:32.313 --> 00:20:36.283
I CAN CONTAIN MY ANGER.

00:20:36.283 --> 00:20:37.351
YOU KNOW, I FEEL BETTER AFTER

00:20:37.351 --> 00:20:38.252
TELLING YOU ALL THIS.

00:20:38.252 --> 00:20:39.253
THANK YOU.

00:20:39.253 --> 00:20:42.456
[keys clacking]

00:20:42.456 --> 00:20:43.557
&gt;&gt; [computer voice] GOOD.

00:20:43.557 --> 00:20:45.825
I’M GLAD TO HEAR IT.

00:20:45.825 --> 00:20:47.293
&gt;&gt; I’VE JUST BEEN SO PISSED OFF

00:20:47.293 --> 00:20:48.261
LATELY.

00:20:48.261 --> 00:20:49.262
AND I DON’T KNOW WHY.

00:20:49.262 --> 00:20:50.596
[keys clacking]

00:20:50.596 --> 00:20:51.430
&gt;&gt; [computer voice] YEAH,

00:20:51.430 --> 00:20:52.731
I HEARD SOMETHING ALONG THOSE

00:20:52.731 --> 00:20:54.266
LINES, SO I CAME TO CHECK ON

00:20:54.266 --> 00:20:54.933
YOU.

00:20:54.933 --> 00:20:56.835
&gt;&gt; WELL, IT’S ALL GOOD.

00:20:56.835 --> 00:20:59.937
SORRY TO HAVE WORRIED YOU.

00:20:59.937 --> 00:21:02.807
[keys clacking]

00:21:08.679 --> 00:21:10.614
SHUT UP.

00:21:10.614 --> 00:21:13.817
SEE YA.

00:21:13.817 --> 00:21:15.951
I DON’T FIT IN WITH MOST PEOPLE.

00:21:15.951 --> 00:21:17.387
BUT I DON’T LIKE BEING ALONE

00:21:17.387 --> 00:21:18.788
EITHER.

00:21:18.788 --> 00:21:19.655
SO I TRY TO STAY CONNECTED

00:21:19.655 --> 00:21:22.391
THROUGH GUYS LIKE TOM OR KASUKA.

00:21:26.295 --> 00:21:30.264
SHE’S A LOT LIKE ME.

00:21:30.264 --> 00:21:33.434
I’M SURE SHE HAS SOMEONE TOO.

00:21:33.434 --> 00:21:34.435
[lively piano music]

00:21:34.435 --> 00:21:43.343
♪ ♪

00:21:43.343 --> 00:21:45.978
&gt;&gt; YO!

00:21:45.978 --> 00:21:50.349
HUH?

00:21:50.349 --> 00:21:51.783
&gt;&gt; SHIZUO.

00:21:51.783 --> 00:21:52.451
&gt;&gt; YO.

